Pattern for Cowl Neck Crop Top as .ai and .dxf. The top swoops lower in the back.   
Made for bust measurement 33&quot;  
There 's a 1&quot; square in the file meant to be used as size reference. Delete accordingly.

This is a credit card sized aircraft.  It is an approximation of a challenger experimental XL-65.   Feel free to share or do what ever you want with it.
If you make it, let me know any comments you have on it.
